WEBVTT

00:08.080 --> 00:10.169
<i>Previously on </i> Cloak and Dagger...

00:10.170 --> 00:11.539
Daddy!

00:11.540 --> 00:12.709
<i>We aren't drilling for oil.</i>

00:12.710 --> 00:14.959
<i>It burned ten times better than oil.</i>

00:14.960 --> 00:17.119
Burns twice as hot. Pumps in the
old rig couldn't handle it.

00:17.120 --> 00:18.829
What gives it that snap?

00:18.830 --> 00:20.579
My secret ingredient: cardamom.

00:20.580 --> 00:21.959
My name's Tandy Bowen.

00:21.960 --> 00:23.119
You knew my dad.

00:28.000 --> 00:29.419
You were there when Billy got shot.

00:29.420 --> 00:30.789
You could tell everyone what you saw.

00:30.790 --> 00:31.829
O'Reilly!

00:31.830 --> 00:33.289
No!

00:33.290 --> 00:35.710
Ty, what's wrong?

